column5: Just applying for my free trail pass for this weekend.........is my license plate number on my skidoo the white sticker with blue numbers?
I was going to print out that same pass for this weekend, except I blew the top end in my Indy 550 today, lol!
Get a 4 stroke and that won't happen.
crappy new Bill!  I printed my free pass yesterday.  Gunna give the trails a shot around her.  Only problem is, my buddies with sleds are running Rev 1000's..  No friggen way I'll be able to keep up
there are speed limits on the trails, so keeping up should be easy

I hit some sections of trails on my fishing trips. I definitely feel safer coming home when its dark....at least there is the chance i might see the headlights of the oncoming #@#%$#@ doing 90mph! Certainly wont be any warning before its too late during daylight hours.
Nah, I'll just have a $1000 repair bill instead of a $100 top end kit     I'll stick to the 2-smoke!
